** Who are we? **

Sentinel Property Group, headquartered in Brisbane, Australia, is a
distinguished Fund and Property Manager with a laser focus on investments in
the thriving Australian commercial property market. Our dynamic portfolio,
worth over $2 billion, spans retail shopping centres, commercial office
buildings, large format retail centres, infrastructure, industrial properties,
hospitality venues, and land.

